# PolyDiff

A machine learning framework for polymer search and analysis, specifically implementing a discrete diffusion model based on the BERT architecture.

## Installation

```bash
pip install -e .
```

## Features

- Discrete diffusion models for polymer generation based on BERT architecture
- Multiple machine learning models support
- Flexible data processing pipeline
- Comprehensive evaluation metrics
